    "actor": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2 due to single-condition testing per ASTM F1717; this shortfall is accepted given the regulatory standard nature of the protocol and the documented risk acceptance note. All three QoIs pass the E/uval < 1.96 and relative error < 10% acceptance criteria. The FEA modeling framework is assessed as credible for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
